parse.title: List of countries by quality of healthcare

text.*:
This is a list of countries by quality of healthcare as published by the Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (OECD).[1]

Contents

  • 1 Outcome of cancer care
    • 1.1 Major cancers
    • 1.2 Female specific cancers
  • 2 Outcome of cardiovascular disease care

Outcome of cancer care[edit]

Major cancers[edit]

The 5-year observed survival rate refers to the percentage of patients who live at least 5 years after being diagnosed with cancer. Many of these patients live much longer than 5 years after diagnosis.
